snippet.title: Sym.BIOS: Torn Asunder - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming Summer 2023 to Steam and Itch.io, a sci-fi visual novel by Cassiopeia Developments.
Wishlist now on Steam!
Sym.BIOS: Torn Asunder is about futuristic utopias, space Colonies, mech fights… But above all, it’s about people. 
Through the lens of 7 exciting characters, discover an epic story told through simple gameplay, vivid dialogue, beautiful art and tricky moral choices. All your decisions will have consequences down the line: will you succeed in your mission?
Music by Sekond Prime featuring Lara Ausensi on vocals, taken from the original soundtrack.
